                              <locus target="#1v">Fol. 1v</locus><desc type="ProtectivePrayer">text of probable protective content. It consists of 5 poorly readable lines. Incipit: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ፆዮ፡ ዸዶ፡ ጸጶ፡ በእሉ፡ ፯ቱ፡ አስማተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ </foreign>etc.</desc>
